OL,3,CPair jailed for 'brutal and senseless'
OL,4,Cmurder of 'much-loved' grandfather
OL,6,FA man and woman have been jailed for
OL,7,Fthe "brutal and senseless murder" of a
OL,8,Fgrandfather in Colwyn Bay.
OL,10,FLauren Harris, 29, and David Webster,
OL,11,F43, murdered 65-year-old Mark Wilcox
OL,12,Fat his home in November last year.
OL,14,FMold Crown Court heard that Mr Wilcox
OL,15,Fhad been in a relationship with Harris
OL,16,Fand had supported her despite
OL,17,Ffinancial difficulties.
