OL,4,Cmurder of 'much-loved' grandfather
OL,6,FThe judge, Mr Justice Edward
OL,7,FPepperall, said Mr Wilcox made the
OL,8,Ffateful decision to invite Harris and
OL,9,Fher friends into his flat to drink and
OL,10,Fsmoke on 19 November 2023.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Harris stabbed Mr
OL,13,FWilcox, puncturing his lung and
OL,14,Fpulmonary artery as well as severely
OL,15,Fbreaking two of his ribs.
OL,17,FThe judge said he was also sure
OL,18,FWebster smashed a vodka bottle on his
OL,19,Fhead.
