OL,6,FHarris and Webster then fled the area
OL,7,Fin a vehicle which was then found
OL,8,Fabandoned.
OL,10,FNorth Wales Police recovered two
OL,11,Fknives from the vehicle and DNA tests
OL,12,Fof the handles showed a link to
OL,13,FWebster.
OL,15,FHarris and Webster had both denied
OL,16,Finvolvement but a jury convicted them
OL,17,Fof murder having heard all the
OL,18,Fevidence.
