OL,6,F"You both callously helped yourself to
OL,7,Fhis car, phone and watches and left
OL,8,Fhim for dead. You gave him no further
OL,9,Fthought as you focussed on your own
OL,10,Fselfish needs".
OL,12,FHarris, who is of no fixed abode but
OL,13,Fis originally from Llandudno, sang
OL,14,FShania Twain's 'Man I Feel Like A
OL,15,FWoman' to herself while the jury were
OL,16,Fout during her trial.
