OL,6,FAfter sentencing, Harris must now
OL,7,Fserve a minimum of 25 years in prison
OL,8,Fand Webster must serve at least 23
OL,9,Fyears before they will be eligible to
OL,10,Fapply for parole.
OL,12,FFollowing their sentence, Webster is
OL,13,Fsaid to called out to Harris: "F******
OL,14,Fpsychopathic bitch. I hope you f***ing
OL,15,Fburn in hell, Lauren".
OL,17,FMr Wilcox was described as a much-
OL,18,Floved father, husband, son, brother
OL,19,Fand grandfather.
