OL,6,FWhile in court, the judge praised Mr
OL,7,FWilcox's grieving relatives in the
OL,8,Fpublic gallery. They suffered
OL,9,Fprovocation during the case but
OL,10,Fremained dignified, he said.
OL,12,FA third man, Thomas Whiteley, 33, of
OL,13,FClos Emlyn, Old Colwyn, was cleared of
OL,14,Fthe killing.
