OL,4,Cmurder of 'much-loved' grandfather
OL,6,FNorth Wales Police's Superintendent
OL,7,FSarah-Jayne Williams, senior
OL,8,Finvestigating officer, said: "This was
OL,9,Fa violent and senseless murder of a
OL,10,Fmuch-loved father, husband, son,
OL,11,Fbrother and grandfather, whose life
OL,12,Fwas taken from him in such unnecessary
OL,13,Fcircumstances.
OL,15,F"His family are suffering profoundly
OL,16,Fdue to their loss, and I recognise
OL,17,Fthat no sentence will bring him back
OL,18,Fto them. However, I hope today's
OL,19,Foutcome will bring some sense of peace.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
