OL,3,CPair jailed for 'brutal and senseless'
OL,4,Cmurder of 'much-loved' grandfather
OL,6,F"They have shown immense courage and
OL,7,Fdignity throughout this complex and
OL,8,Flengthy investigation, and my thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with them today.
OL,11,F"Harris and Webster callously murdered
OL,12,FMark in his own home in a sustained
OL,13,Fattack, where he should have been
OL,14,Fsafe. They took his belongings,
OL,15,Fincluding his car, which Harris
OL,16,Fsubsequently crashed.
OL,18,F"They have prolonged his family's
OL,19,Fsuffering by refusing to admit their
OL,20,Fpart in killing Mark, whilst showing
OL,21,Fno remorse for their actions.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
