OL,6,F"As a family, we have been left
OL,7,Fabsolutely devastated. Mark's
OL,8,Fgrandchildren will grow up without
OL,9,Ftheir doting and loving grandfather.
OL,11,F"Mark's death leaves a void that feels
OL,12,Firreparable. Things will never be the
OL,13,Fsame again."
